<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الثَّاقِبُ}</span> ... المُضِيءُ المُتَوَهِّجُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنْ كُلُّ نَفْسٍ لَّمَّا}</span> ... مَا كُلُّ نَفْسٍ إِلَّا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَافِظٌ}</span> ... مَلَكٌ يَحْفَظُ أَعْمَالَهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دَافِقٍ}</span> ... مُنْصَبٍّ بِسُرْعَةٍ فِي الرَّحِمِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصُّلْبِ}</span> ... الظَّهْرِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالتَّرَائِبِ}</span> ... عِظَامِ الصَّدْرِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَجْعِهِ}</span> ... رَدِّهِ حَيًّا بَعْدَ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُبْلَى السَّرَائِرُ}</span> ... تُخْتَبَرُ، وَتُكْشَفُ ضَمَائِرُ القُلُوبِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الرَّجْعِ}</span> ... صَاحِبَةِ المَطَرِ المُتَكَرِّرِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
